    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S54B32 inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies to deliver immediate throttle response up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed by a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, addressing common chassis fatigue points. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative steering feel these cars are known for. While showing signs of honest use, the drivetrain and structural integrity make this a premier candidate for the discerning enthusiast.",
